title: YouTube Jail Release Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Your new set up looks great, the better lighting makes you look 10 years younger despite your health problems lately. Get well soon.
I missed livestream but catching the replay! 💕💕💕

I'm soooooo happy that you're out of #YouTubeJail !!! Setup looks Awesome! Sounds really good too! 🎙🔊📽🎬
Happy Solstice! Happy holidays and look forward to seeing you again soon! 😍🍀🍀🍀

Hey MaryGirl. Good to see you back. Looking forward to new stuff ;)!!. I also finished watching season 8 and I have to say that in the end I was disappointed with it. In the end it just became Coven 2 and I didn't like that. In my opinion a cross-over doesn't mean rehashing old stuff. I would have rather liked it if Ryan Murphy just kept it small. Like the Murder House stuff in season 8. That was only 2 episodes which is fine and I think it would have been better if they did that with the witches as well and just focus more on the new characters.
By the way................have you watched The Haunting Of Hill House yet ??. If not you should try it out !. It's awesome !!
